	<LINE>Four-fifths, or Eighty per cent., of the Profits are divisible, according to the Company's</LINE>
	<LINE>Deed of Settlement, amongst Insurers on the Participatory Scale. Tlie Policies of these</LINE>
	<LINE>Assurers are immediately interested in the Profits.</LINE>
	<LINE>Policies assigned are not forfeited by Duelling, Suicide, or the execution of Judicial Sentences.</LINE>
	<LINE>Every facility is given on moderate terms to persons going beyond the prescribed limits of their</LINE>
	<LINE>Policies. No charge is made for residence in many Colonies and Foreign States. Post-Office</LINE>
	<LINE>Officials assured at Reduced Rates, under a special arrangement with Her Majesty's Postmaster-</LINE>
