	<LINE>EIRE DEPARTMENT.</LINE>
	<LINE>The Company grants Insurances on property in all parts of the United Kingdom at the</LINE>
	<LINE>lowest Rates of Premium corresponding to the Risk.</LINE>
	<LINE>All Policies issued by the Company include the Risk of Explosion occasioned by Gas, without</LINE>
	<LINE>extra charge.</LINE>
